{"word":"G366 - ἀνανήφω - ananḗphō - an-an-ay'-fo - Recover self","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀνανήφω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">ananḗphō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">an-an-ay'-fo</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Recover self</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - மயக்கந்தெளி"},{"paragraph":"to return to soberness"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G303 - ἀνά - aná - an-ah'/303\">G303</a> and <a href=\"#/G3525 - νήφω - nḗphō - nay'-fo/3525\">G3525</a>; to become <i>sober again</i>, that is, (figuratively) <i>regain</i> (one&rsquo;s) <i>senses:</i> - recover self.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}